    <section id="dita_contextual_menu_actions">
      <title>JATS Contextual Menu Actions</title>
      <p>The following actions are available in the contextual menu when editing in
          <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode (most of them are also available in the
          <uicontrol>JATS</uicontrol> menu at the top of the interface):</p>
      <p>
        <dl>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/add-file-to-content-fusion"
            product="author editor">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Attribute16.gif" id="image_cm5_sdt_yjb"/>Edit
                Attributes</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Displays an <xref
                href="author-attributes-view.dita#author-attributes-view/in-place-attr-editor"
                >in-place attributes editor</xref> that allows you to manage the attributes of an
              element.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/edit_profiling_attributes">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/action-cut">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/action-copy">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/action-paste">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/edit-image-map">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/BoxedText16.png" id="image_ucg_smn_zjb"/>Boxed
                Text</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts or wraps content in a box with a shaded background.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol>Insert</uicontrol> submenu</dt>
            <dd>
              <p>This submenu includes the following insert actions:</p>
              <p>
                <dl>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol>Figure</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Inserts a <xmlelement>fig</xmlelement> element with a
                        <xmlelement>title</xmlelement> (inside a <xmlelement>caption</xmlelement>
                      element). This action opens a dialog box that allows you to enter the text for
                      the title for the figure.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol>Graphic Figure</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Inserts a <xmlelement>fig</xmlelement> element with a
                        <xmlelement>title</xmlelement> (inside a <xmlelement>caption</xmlelement>
                      element), and a <xmlelement>graphic</xmlelement> element. A dialog box is
                      displayed that allows you to enter the title for the figure, followed by a
                      dialog box that allows you to select the URL of the graphic to be
                      inserted.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DisplayQuote16.png" id="image_axz_vmn_zjb"
                        />Display Quote</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Inserts or wraps content in a <xmlelement>disp-quote</xmlelement>
                      element.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Paragraph16.png" id="image_g2g_bdt_yjb"
                        />Insert Paragraph</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Inserts a new <term>paragraph</term> element at current cursor
                      position.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/insert-image-dlentry">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol>Insert Entity</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Allows you to insert a predefined entity or character entity. Surrogate
                      character entities (range #x10000 to #x10FFFF) are also accepted. Character
                      entities can be entered in one of the following forms: <ul id="ul_t3w_twm_ps">
                        <li>#<i>&lt;decimal value&gt;</i> - e.g. #65</li>
                        <li>&amp;#<i>&lt;decimal value&gt;</i> - e.g. &amp;#65</li>
                        <li>#x<i>&lt;hexadecimal value&gt;</i> - e.g. #x41</li>
                        <li>&amp;#x<i>&lt;hexadecimal value&gt;</i> - e.g. &amp;#x41</li>
                      </ul></dd>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl>
              </p>
            </dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt>Style submenu</dt>
            <dd>This submenu includes the following text styling actions:<p>
                <dl>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Monospace16.png" id="image_cxm_dnn_zjb"
                        />Monospace</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Inserts or wraps content with a <xmlelement>monospace</xmlelement>
                      element.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/bold-dlentry">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/italic-dlentry">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/underline-dlentry">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl>
              </p></dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><menucascade>
                <uicontrol><image href="../img/UnorderedList16.png" id="image_p2f_mnn_zjb"
                  />List</uicontrol>
                <uicontrol><image href="../img/UnorderedList16.png" id="image_gmh_3nn_zjb"/>Insert
                  Unordered List</uicontrol>
              </menucascade></dt>
            <dd>Inserts an unordered list at the cursor position. A child list item is also
              automatically inserted by default. You can also use this action to convert selected
              paragraphs or other types of lists to an unordered list.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><menucascade>
                <uicontrol><image href="../img/UnorderedList16.png" id="image_l53_nnn_zjb"
                  />List</uicontrol>
                <uicontrol><image href="../img/OrderedList16.png" id="image_h2t_3nn_zjb"/>Insert
                  Ordered List</uicontrol>
              </menucascade></dt>
            <dd>Inserts an ordered list at the cursor position. A child list item is also
              automatically inserted by default. You can also use this action to convert selected
              paragraphs or other types of lists to an ordered list.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Code16.png" id="image_znz_4nn_zjb"
              />Code</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Inserts or wraps content in a <xmlelement>code</xmlelement> element.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-author-actions/select-submenu">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol>Text</uicontrol> submenu</dt>
            <dd>
              <p>This submenu contains the following actions:</p>
              <p>
                <dl id="ul_ckk_ftc_gd">
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol>To Lower Case</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Converts the selected content to lower case characters.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol>To Upper Case</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Converts the selected content to upper case characters.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol>Capitalize Sentences</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Converts to upper case the first character of every selected sentence.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol>Capitalize Words</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Converts to upper case the first character of every selected word.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry>
                    <dt><uicontrol>Count Words</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Counts the number of words and characters (no spaces) in the entire document
                      or in the selection for regular content and read-only content. <note>The
                        content marked as deleted with <xref keyref="glossentry_track-changes"
                            ><term>change tracking</term></xref> is ignored when counting
                        words.</note></dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/convert_hex_to_char">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl>
              </p>
            </dd>
          </dlentry>
